Sentencas: Due to its high conversion efficiency in fuel-to-power and power-to-fuel modes, reversible solid oxide cell (RSOC) is widely regarded as a promising device.
Titulo: Enhanced electrochemical redox kinetics of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 in reversible solid oxide cells

Sentencas: In this study, La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.7M0.1O3 (M=Fe, Mo, Nb) oxides are prepared and composited with Sm0.2Ce0.8O2-(Li0.67Na0.33)2CO3 to form reversible single component cell (RSCC).
Titulo: Enhanced electrochemical redox kinetics of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 in reversible solid oxide cells

Sentencas: Among them, La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.7Mo0.1O3 (LSCFM) shows the highest oxygen vacancy concentration, further promoting catalytic activity towards oxygen reduction reaction (ORR) and hydrogen oxidation reaction (HOR).
Titulo: Enhanced electrochemical redox kinetics of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 in reversible solid oxide cells

Sentencas: Besides, Mo or Nb doping enhances the surface reaction rate constant (kchem) and oxygen chemical bulk diffusion coefficient (Dchem) at the temperature range of 550-700 degrees C. LSCFM shows the highest kchem of 39.3 x 10-5 cm s- 1 , approximate 3.5 times as 11.1 x 10-5 cm s- 1 for La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 (LSCF), and Dchem for LSCFM is 31.1 x 10-6 cm2 s- 1 , approximate 2.5 times as 12.4 x 10-6 cm2 s- 1 for LSCF at 700 degrees
Titulo: Enhanced electrochemical redox kinetics of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 in reversible solid oxide cells

Sentencas: C. Furthermore, the rate determining steps (RDS) of ORR and HOR for LSCFM-based cell are the reduction of oxygen atoms to O- and the charge transfer reaction, respectively.
Titulo: Enhanced electrochemical redox kinetics of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 in reversible solid oxide cells

Sentencas: Under SOFC/SOEC reversible operation, the RSCC composed of LSCFM exhibits the best cell performance.
Titulo: Enhanced electrochemical redox kinetics of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 in reversible solid oxide cells

Sentencas: In the solid oxide fuel cell mode, the maximum power density reaches 236.2 mW cm-2 and in the solid oxide electrolysis cell mode the current density at 1.3 V is-312.4 mA cm- 2.
Titulo: Enhanced electrochemical redox kinetics of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.2Fe0.8O3 in reversible solid oxide cells
